 Valtron had the two destrons and the three horsmen clear the field where the 
ark had laied. It had taken quite some time but it was worth it. He looked it 
over and there was no depre whats so ever. "Ok we are ready to start the 
base. Preds you pull our the braceing cables and Destrons you help them. 
Connect them all to form the outer skeleton of the bottom of the ship. 
Maximals..after they are finished I must have youput on the outside first 
layer of concret. Then we shall put on the three diffrent layers of mettalic 
codeing." the destrons and preds quickly started on the bracing cables...
